1950;;The Showdown;;American;;Dorrell McGowan;;Walter Brennan, Marie Windsor;;western;;https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/The_Showdown_(1950_film);;A former Texas lawman. Shadrach Jones (William Elliott) sets out to discover who killed his brother and stole their combined savings. While at the saloon run by the beautiful Adelaide (Marie Windsor), Jones becomes convinced that the thieving murderer is one of a group of cowboys on a cattle drive led by Captain MacKellar (Walter Brennan). Determined to find justice, Jones joins the cattle drive and slowly gets closer to uncovering the identity of the killer.